  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  Men or women between the ages of 18 and 75&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  Clinical diagnosis of autoimmune thyroiditis, serum TPOAb and TGAB positive&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  Thyroid function is normal, and no drugs affecting thyroid function such as Umetole&#xD;
             and Serge have been used&#xD;
&#xD;
        Exclusion Criteria:&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  The contraindications indicated in the Chinese instructions of the drug&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  Hypothyroidism, hyperthyroidism&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  Liver function impairment&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  Renal function impairment&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  Claustrophobia&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  Mental disorders&#xD;
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
